                        <interp inst="t18410705-name-717" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES DREWETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a dealer in coals, and live in Gibraltar-row, Southwark. I saw Scott on a Tuesday or Wednesday in June, buy a mare of the prisoner—he gave one guinea and a half, and another horse, in change—the prisoner said he had bought the mare of a man named Reeves, at Kennington.</p>
